						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 10.5 10.5 7.5v9l5.25-3v-3Z"/>
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z"/>
					</svg>
					<p class="text-sm text-text-secondary font-medium">Demo video coming soon</p>
					<p class="text-xs">See ContextAgora in action with Soundmurai's live database</p>
				</div> -->
			</div>

			<!-- MAAT -->
			<div class="border border-accent/20 bg-bg-raised px-6 py-8 sm:px-8">
				<a href="https://maatapp.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group flex items-center gap-4 mb-5 w-fit hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity">
					<img src="/logos/maat.svg" alt="MAAT logo" class="w-14 h-14 shrink-0" width="56" height="56" loading="lazy" />
					<span class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-text tracking-tight">MAAT</span>
					<svg class="w-4 h-4 text-text-muted -mb-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 6H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 3 8.25v10.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 5.25 21h10.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 18 18.75V10.5m-10.5 6L21 3m0 0h-5.25M21 3v5.25" /></svg>
				</a>
				<p class="text-sm text-text-muted uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Gym management for BJJ, MMA & martial arts</p>
				<blockquote class="text-lg text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-3">
					"We went from spending hours digging through member data to having our AI surface exactly what we need in seconds. ContextAgora made that possible."
				</blockquote>
				<p class="text-xs text-text-muted mb-6">— Bernat, AI Engineer at MAAT</p>
				<div class="bg-bg border border-border px-4 py-3 text-xs">
					<span class="text-accent font-medium">User asks →</span>
					<span class="text-text italic ml-1">"Which members haven't renewed their subscription this month?"</span>
				</div>
				<!-- <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed border-l-2 border-accent/30 pl-4 mb-5">
					MAAT manages members, payments, classes, and belt progressions for martial arts gyms. Their team used to dig through data manually to answer routine questions. Now their AI pulls the answers in seconds.
				</p>
				<ol class="space-y-2.5 mb-6">
					{[
						'The agent locates the relevant context module for member data',
						'It reads the schema and understands how members and subscriptions relate',
						'It generates a query to retrieve members with lapsed renewals',
						'It filters and returns the matching list',
						'It delivers a clear answer the team can act on immediately',
					].map((step, i) => (
						<li class="flex gap-3 items-start text-sm text-text-secondary">
